birthdayflower.name: Floral Embrace™
birthdayflower.description: Like a warm embrace, our vibrant flower bouquet delivers your sentiments to someone special. A rich gathering of yellow and orange blooms, with pops of bright pink and purple, it's more than a gift…it's a way to express how you feel inside.

birthdayflower.name: Assorted Tulip Bouquet
birthdayflower.description: Our colorful tulips are an instant day-brightener. Whoever they’re for, whatever the reason, this cheerful bunch of spring blooms is the best kind of surprise.

birthdayflower.name: Red Roses
birthdayflower.description: Radiant. Timeless. Romantic. There’s something so special about our red roses, especially how loved they’ll feel when a farm-fresh gathering of blooms arrives at their door.

birthdayflower.name: Lovely Lavender Medley™
birthdayflower.description: Lovely memories are made with thoughtful gifts for the ones we care about. Our charming lavender flower bouquet is loosely gathered with a medley of lavender & white blooms. Hand-designed inside a clear cylinder vase with cascading greenery all around, it’s a wonderful way to express the sentiments you have inside your heart.

birthdayflower.name: Magnificent Pink Rose & Lily Bouquet
birthdayflower.description: Magnificent is the only way to describe our all-pink bouquet. We’ve gathered one dozen long-stem roses with six, multi-bloomed Asiatic lilies for a gift that’s sure to leave an impression.

birthdayflower.name: Assorted Roses & Peruvian Lilies
birthdayflower.description: Help brighten someone’s day with our lively bouquet. Filled with roses and Peruvian lilies, this colorful mix of blooms is a wonderful way to reach out and show you care, for the big milestones and “just because” moments.

birthdayflower.name: Fields Of Europe® Bliss
birthdayflower.description: That feeling of bliss, captured in a bouquet. Inspired by the beauty of the European countryside, our best seller brings together radiant roses and lush lilies in a glass vase wrapped in red ribbon. Whatever your reason for reaching out, it’s a gift that delivers on delight.

birthdayflower.name: Classic Budding Rose
birthdayflower.description: Our pink rose plant is a true classic. Designed in a rose-patterned planter with an elegant gold scalloped rim, it brings timeless beauty to the home or garden. Complement your gift by adding our rose-scented Yankee Candle® on its own or bundled with soothing hand lotion from Camille Beckman® in a signature floral fragrance.

birthdayflower.name: Yellow Roses
birthdayflower.description: Fill someone’s day with sunshine with our vibrant yellow roses. These bright, cheerful blooms are a warm, thoughtful gift that will leave them beaming, whatever the occasion.

birthdayflower.name: Sunflower Bouquet
birthdayflower.description: Make every day brighter with our abundant bouquet of fresh sunflowers. These radiant, long-lasting blooms bring that just-picked-from-the-meadow feeling to birthdays, get well wishes, or any day you want to make someone you care about smile

birthdayflower.name: Garden of Grandeur®
birthdayflower.description: Designed to be as unforgettable as the person who receives it. Our luxurious arrangement of colorful, fresh-from-the-garden blooms is artistically arranged in a chic glass vase by our expert florists to create the ultimate wow gift for someone who means the world to you.

birthdayflower.name: Ultimate Elegance™ Long Stem Assorted Roses
birthdayflower.description: Our rainbow of long stem roses is the ultimate surprise for letting someone know how you feel. Two, three or four dozen blooms in a of stunning array of colors are artistically arranged by our expert florists inside an elegant glass vase and personally hand-delivered to help you beautifully express what’s in your heart.

birthdayflower.name: Pretty In Pink Azalea
birthdayflower.description: Send along a pretty spring surprise. Our pink azalea plant arrives budding and ready to bloom in a charming pink & white planter, with flower-shaped cutouts and the words “Flowers & Garden” front and center. Make it extra special by adding our sparkling pink crystal heart wind chime to your gift.
